# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Portfolio hygiene — test artefacts, captures & local scratch.
# The code is versioned; derived data, screenshots and media are not.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Playwright / MCP capture artefacts
.playwright-mcp/

# Visual-QA screenshots & scratch dumps at the repo root
/*.png
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.yml
/*.txt
/*.json
!/package.json
!/package-lock.json
/snapshot*.md
/snap*.md

